How to publish (Netlify Drop â€“ FREE)
1. Zip the SmartKidsClub folder (SmartKidsClub.zip).
2. Go to https://app.netlify.com/drop
3. Drag & drop SmartKidsClub.zip â€” Netlify will upload and publish a site.
4. Replace placeholder MP3s in assets/audio/ with real .mp3 files (keep same filenames).
5. To change PayPal email, edit the donate link in HTML files (search for "paypal.com/donate").

